<title>zhǔ a wǒ děng hòu nǐ 迦南1065</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wǒ děng hòu nǐ, zhǔ a wǒ děng hòu nǐ.
 zài gāo gāo de shān dǐng, zài shēn shēn de yōu gǔ, wǒ děng hòu nǐ, wǒ děng hòu nǐ.
 zhǔ a wǒ jìng bài nǐ, zhǔ a wǒ jìng bài nǐ.
 zài shùn jìng de rì zi lǐ, zài jiān nán de rì zi lǐ, wǒ jìng bài nǐ, wǒ jìng bài nǐ.</lyrics>
</song>